alerts.text: From Saturday 29 February, the city-bound bus stop on Victoria Rd opposite Hornsey St (203916) will be relocated north of Roberts St until the completion of the Rozelle Interchange in 2023.
alerts.title: Victoria Rd, Rozelle bus stop relocation

alerts.text:
From Sunday 18 August until the end of November 2020 the westbound bus stops on Victoria Rd at Lilyfield Rd (203919) and at Hornsey St (203920) will be closed due to demolition works for the Rozelle Interchange. 

The alternative stop for both closed stops is on Victoria Rd before Maney St (203921). 

Bus route 433, 501, 502, 504, 506, 507, 508, 515, 518, 520, L37, M50, M52 and Special Event Bus 2 will be impacted. 

Signs will be in place at closed stops with directions to the alternative stop.
alerts.title: Rozelle bus stop temporary closures
